asset_contract.name: PartyDegenerates
asset_contract.description:
Party Degenerates are a collection of 10,000 NFTs representing the rebellious spirit of those who choose to celebrate life, rather than merely living it.

They are professional misfits, have a big heart, like to party, and are crazy enough to think they can change the world. They have flown under the radar, searching for like-minded creatives, artists, musicians, builders, and believers who dare to express their truth in a society that increasingly values rules and conformity.

A mind-blowing roster of prominent digital artists and emerging talents in the broader NFT community have united to unleash the Party Degenerates under a single generative art project. Visit www.partydegenerates.com for more info.
